      "description": "This specimen represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring a high-revving power unit with direct fuel injection and a lightning-fast dual-clutch transmission. The chassis remains exceptionally taut, benefiting from active suspension management and a mechanical limited-slip differential that ensures surgical power delivery. Every bushing is factory-firm, and the engine maintains factory-spec compression across all cylinders with zero fluid seepage. The aerodynamic profile is unblemished, preserving the integrity of the underbody diffusers and active rear spoiler. This is a concours-ready example for the discerning driver who demands mechanical perfection.",
